---
title: Chive Double Chicken and Wild Rice with Buttery Green Beans
description: A classic 1-2-3 meal is sometimes all you need to please the whole family. Buttery green beans, savoury wild rice and chive-seasoned chicken are what you'll find in this elevated weeknight chicken dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-double-a-la-ciboulette-et-riz-sauvage-aedbb5bd.jpg
